block history
  if userDetail.isAdmin
    p You are administrator
  p. 
    This page lists your already terminated jobs from the 10 last days.
    You can select another date in the field below.
  div(id='div_start_date', class='input-append date')
     input(type='text', name='startDate', class='span2', id='startDate')
     span.add-on
        i.icon-th
  if userDetail.isAdmin
     div(id='div_history_user')
        p username
        select(name='historyUser', class='span2', id='historyUser')
  #historyTable
  br
  p Page opened 
    abbr.timeago.loaded

block applications
  h2 Applications on the cluster
  p
    | Have a look 
    a(href='https://baobabmaster.unige.ch/enduser/src/enduser/enduser.html#modules' target='_blank') here
    |  to know how to use most of the applications on the cluster using "modules".
  #appsTable
  br
  p Page opened
    abbr.timeago.loaded

